data.description: Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this charming Covington, GA home. With 5 bedrooms and 3 full baths, this property offers plenty of space for the whole family! The open living spaces are bathed in natural light, complete with vaulted ceilings and a cozy fireplace that sets the stage for relaxing evenings. The spacious kitchen and living room lead to the oversized deck overlooking a private wooded back yard with a generous 1.25-acre lot nestled on a peaceful cul-de-sac street. This home offers both privacy and room to roam. The basement holds endless possibilities and a side entrance garage for added convenience! Great house close to the new Eastside high school.
